## Work Stream 3 — Real Build Execution

### Strategy
Inject `ITerminalService` into `BuildSystemService`. When `build()` or `flash()` is called, create (or reuse) a named terminal instance `"Firmware Build"` and call `sendText(command.join(' '), true)` to actually execute the command. Parse stdout/stderr lines through the existing `_parseBuildOutput()` method already in the service.

### Key API
```typescript
// terminal.ts:36 — already in the codebase
export const ITerminalService = createDecorator<ITerminalService>('terminalService');
// terminal.ts:899
sendText(text: string, shouldExecute: boolean): Promise<void>;
```

